The paper discusses the forensic investigation of cloud storage environments and the use of forensic tools to recover data from end-devices such as smartphones. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses data synchronization and storage (cs.DL), cybercrime (cs.CY), and software engineering (cs.SE) in the context of forensic investigation.
